claim.claim-text:
A method of manufacturing a composite substrate, comprising:
forming a dent portion in a second region between a plurality of first regions on a main surface of a silicon substrate;
forming a metal layer on at least one of the main surface of the silicon substrate and a support substrate having electrical insulating property;
bonding the main surface of the silicon substrate onto the support substrate through the metal layer; and
heating the support substrate and the silicon substrate bonded with each other configured for aggregating the metal layer in the dent portion and forming an amorphous form containing silicon and a metal which forms the metal layer on the main surface of the silicon substrate which is located at a side of the support substrate.
